{"tid":2006024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★TVB《足球小將》小志強御用配音員疑不獲續約 月底離職","createTime":"2020-05-07T13:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T13:54:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a7b44e4689ef9feb5ce68d07d1f37a959c016e76","tid":2006024,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:20:30.000Z","msg":"近日再有消息傳出，曾經聲演動畫《聖鬥士星矢》星矢、《龍貓》怕醜仔、《足球小將》小志強、《龍珠》笛子魔童、《美少女戰士》地場衛（安迪美奧）、《數碼暴龍》城戶丈、《百變小櫻Magic咭》木之本桃矢及《喜羊羊與灰太狼》灰太狼等等的資深配音員馮錦堂，將不被大台續約，將於本月底離開這個工作超過40年的地方。人稱堂哥的馮錦堂於1979年入讀第8期無綫電視藝員訓練班，畢業後加入無綫電視配音組，乃目前電視台中最資深配音員之一。<br />\n<br />\n堂哥不被續約的消息，在不少關於動漫配音的FB專頁瘋傳，有人留言大讚堂哥的聲音很好聽，感謝他帶給大家一個美好的童年回憶，還有人說：「堂哥喺《足球小將中學編》有一句對白我好深刻，就係南葛對東邦果陣講：『志偉，我已經輸夠畀你你喇！！！』」亦有人說：「堂哥配剛柔角色都可以，我最深刻係佢配《黃金戰士》主角小龍及高迪安！」翻查無綫的官方網頁，在配音藝人的一欄上，仍然見到堂哥的名字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200505/OP4KQR5CNY5E2BOZI3YHB2MXTA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1rj3b1oBvXhA2KN0W04TGnrvMtzKxM0rSYfOcjBnA_4HLf3NoQwfro3hI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200505%2FOP4KQR5CNY5E2BOZI3YHB2MXTA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1rj3b1oBvXhA2KN0W04TGnrvMtzKxM0rSYfOcjBnA_4HLf3NoQwfro3hI&d=kJsi%2B77Adq7yP7dZlTZe0JzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=49c62788\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200505%2FOP4KQR5CNY5E2BOZI3YHB2MXTA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1rj3b1oBvXhA2KN0W04TGnrvMtzKxM0rSYfOcjBnA_4HLf3NoQwfro3hI&h=f614ee10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200505/OP4KQR5CNY5E2BOZI3YHB2MXTA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailye